What Is The Sunsai Electric Scooter?


The Sunsai Electric Scooter is an electric scooter designed for young riders. It's powered by a 1200-watt motor and has a top speed of 30 and above KM per hour, making it perfect for short commutes or leisurely rides. The scooter features a lightweight MS frame, which makes it easy to carry around when not in use. It also has a range of up to 100 KM on a single charge, which is more than enough for most riders.

