3. Great Range And Speed

The Sunsai Electric Scooter has a decent range of up to 100 KM on a single charge, which is more than enough for most riders. It also has a top speed of 30 KM per hour, making it perfect for short commutes or leisurely rides. However, it's important to note that riders should always wear protective gear and follow the recommended speed limits.

4. Eco-Friendly

The Sunsai Electric Scooter is powered by a 1200-watt motor, which is eco-friendly and sustainable. By using this electric scooter, riders can reduce their carbon footprint and contribute to a cleaner and healthier environment.

